title: Lift Up Your Heads
verses:
Lift up your heads and the doors of your heart
And the King of glory will come in
(Repeat)

Who is this King of Glory?
The Lord strong and mighty!
Who is this King of Glory?
The Lord, mighty in battle!

Who is this King of Glory?
Jesus our Messiah!
Who is this King of Glory?
Jesus, Lord of Lords!
